data.description: Welcome to your new home in Chelsea, Alabama! It's tucked away on a quiet street, sitting on a big 3-acre lot with lots of space for you to enjoy. You might even see some deer or an owl wandering around the yard—it's like having your own little piece of nature! When you step outside onto the back patio or the screened porch, you'll feel how peaceful and calm it is. It's the perfect spot to relax and unwind after a long day. Inside, the main floor has a big living room and a separate dining area, perfect for having friends and family over. The kitchen is spacious and has a cool island in the middle. Plus, the floors are all shiny hardwood, giving the whole place a classy feel.There are three bedrooms on this floor, including the master bedroom, and a handy laundry room, too. Downstairs, there's another bedroom, a full bathroom, and a cozy living area with a fireplace. You can even step right outside from there! The best part You don't need to do a thing--this home is ready for YOU!
